(6, 1724, 'Kierstin (Stitch\'s manager)', 'kierstin@kierstinbuchner.com', 'http://www.kierstinbuchner.com', '24.21.140.136', '2009-07-16 17:37:57', '2009-07-16 22:37:57', 'Just a few days in the city, and already you\'re famous!  You were too big for Roseburg, and you knew it.  Welcome to Dogtown, little man!', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
