(48, 1, '2014-10-18 17:34:08', '2014-10-18 17:34:08', '<h2>Payment</h2>\r\n\r\nAcceptable forms of payment include VISA, MasterCard, American Express and Discover. These are processed directly through our checkout page or via PayPal if you choose that option. Our site is secured by Geotrust. Click the logo below to verify security details.\r\n\r\n<!-- GeoTrust QuickSSL [tm] Smart  Icon tag. Do not edit. -->\r\n<script language="javascript" type="text/javascript" src="//smarticon.geotrust.com/si.js"></script>\r\n<!-- end  GeoTrust Smart Icon tag -->\r\n\r\n<h2>Sales Tax</h2>\r\n\r\nelsa+sam is located in Oregon; therefore, we charge no sales tax.\r\n\r\n<h2>Shipping &amp; Returns</h2>\r\n\r\nAll items are shipped via USPS Priority mail, unless otherwise requested and available. Shipping costs include insurance to make sure pieces arrive safely and in one piece. Please allow 1-2 weeks for normal delivery. Occasionally items may be oversold; in those cases we will ship backorder items once we receive them, or we will have items shipped directly from the warehouse. Sometimes items ordered together may not be shipped together, in which case we will contact you right away.\r\n\r\nIf items are damaged during shipping, please contact us within 10 days of receipt. If the item is replaceable, we will send out a replacement. If it is no longer available, you will receive full a refund of the item.\r\n\r\n<strong>We do ship internationally</strong>. Rates vary by country. Please send us an email that includes your full shipping address at: <a href="mailto:info@elsasam.com">info@elsasam.com</a> and we will get back to you as quickly as possible.\r\n\r\n<h2>Return Policy</h2>\r\n\r\nMerchandise purchased from elsasam.com may be returned for credit or exchange within 14 days of purchase if in original condition and packaging and is accompanied with receipt. Store credit is valid for one year from date of issue. Shipping costs will not be refunded or credited. All costs for return shipment are the responsibility of the customer. <a href="/contact/">Click here</a> to contact us to initiate the return process.\r\n\r\nOnline purchases may be canceled within 24 hours.', 'Store Policies', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'store-policies', '', '', '2014-11-19 19:14:46', '2014-11-19 19:14:46', '', 0, 'http://elsasam.local/?page_id=48', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(49, 1, '2014-10-18 17:34:08', '2014-10-18 17:34:08', '<h2>\r\n	Payment</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	We use PayPal for processing credit card payments. If you have trouble making a payment through PayPal, please let us know so that we can make other arrangements for your order. <strong>Note that you do not need a PayPal account in order to use PayPal.&nbsp; If you prefer to make a payment over the phone, we accept VISA, MC, American Express &amp; Discover. </strong></p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Sales Tax</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	elsa+sam is located in Oregon, therefore we charge no sales tax.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Shipping &amp; Returns</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	All items are shipped via USPS Priority mail, unless otherwise requested and available. Shipping costs include insurance to make sure pieces arrive safely and in one piece. Please allow 1-2 weeks for normal delivery. Occasionally items may be oversold, therefore we will ship backorder items once we receive them or have items shipped directly from the warehouse. Sometimes items ordered together may not be shipped together, in which we will contact you right away if this is the case.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	If items are damaged during shipping, please contact us immediately so we can file a claim with the appropriate shipping vendor. If the item is replaceable, we will send out a replacement. If it is no longer available, you will receive full refund of the item.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>We do ship internationally</strong>. Rates vary by country. Please send us an email that includes your shipping address at: <a href="mailto:info@elsasam.com">info@elsasam.com</a> and we will get back to you as quickly as possible.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Live in Portland, OR? We do offer free pick up. Please send us an email that you’d like to pick up your order.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>*We offer FREE shipping in the US on all orders when you spend $100 or more!</strong></p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Return Policy</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	Merchandise purchased from elsasam.com may be returned for credit or exchange within 30 days of purchase if in original condition and packaging and is accompanied with receipt. Store credit is valid for one year from date of issue. Shipping costs will not be refunded or credited. All costs for return shipment are the responsibility of the customer. <a href="index.php?route=account/return/insert">Click here and fill out the form</a> to initiate the return process.&nbsp;Please contact us if you have any questions.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Online purchases may be canceled within 24 hours.</p>\r\n', 'Terms & Conditions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '48-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-18 17:34:08', '2014-10-18 17:34:08', '', 48, 'http://elsasam.local/48-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
