(1480, 2, '2009-05-29 14:21:10', '2009-05-29 19:21:10', 'Yay! This is my very first posting on this blog. Whew. Thanks for being brave enough to stop in. I\'ve been terrible about updating my website so I thought this would be a great way to inform everyone of new products when they arrive, gift ideas, great finds and events.\n\n<img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1490" title="choco" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/choco-550x365.jpg" alt="choco" width="550" height="365" />\n\nIn the meantime, enjoy these lovely pieces by Suki Allen. We are going to be having a one year anniversary party for the store this June and we\'ll be featuring more of Suki\'s work.\n\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1483" title="bird" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/bird-199x300.jpg" alt="bird" width="199" height="300" /> <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1485" title="bird2" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/bird2-217x300.jpg" alt="bird2" width="217" height="300" /> <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1488" title="bird3" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/bird3-206x300.jpg" alt="bird3" width="206" height="300" /> <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1492" title="bird4" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/bird4-280x300.jpg" alt="bird4" width="280" height="300" />', 'Welcome!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'welcome', '', '', '2009-05-29 14:21:10', '2009-05-29 19:21:10', '', 0, 'http://www.elsasam.com/?p=1480', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1499, 2, '2009-05-30 16:36:06', '2009-05-30 21:36:06', 'These adorable salt &amp; pepper shakers by Lola Goldstein are too hard to pass up. Whether you are looking for a fun gift for the wedding couple, birthday friend, or simply a nice touch for your kitchen, these shakers will definitely do the trick! Made by Lola Goldstein in her studio in Buenos Aires, Argentina. Special and very sweet.\n\n[caption id="attachment_1502" align="alignnone" width="550" caption="Salt &amp; Pepper shakers - $36.00"]<img class="size-large wp-image-1502" title="dsc_44771" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/dsc_44771-550x358.jpg" alt="Salt &amp; Pepper shakers - $36.00" width="550" height="358" />[/caption]\n\nCirca Ceramics\' color, design and quality always makes me happy. These 16 oz bowls are perfect for berries and a nice scoop (or two) of ice cream.\n\n[caption id="attachment_1505" align="alignnone" width="482" caption="16 oz bowls - $34.00 each"]<img class="size-large wp-image-1505" title="dsc_4481" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/dsc_4481-482x550.jpg" alt="16 oz bowls - $34 each" width="482" height="550" />[/caption]\n\nThese adorable sushi plates by Swedish design group, Defyra, are a great gift for someone who loves simplicity and design.\n\n[caption id="attachment_1511" align="alignnone" width="550" caption="Sushi plates -$28.00 each"]<img class="size-large wp-image-1511" title="dsc_4510" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/dsc_4510-550x313.jpg" alt="Sushi plates -$28.00 each" width="550" height="313" />[/caption]\n\nLinens are always "safe" and a great gift for anyone who spends a lot of time in the kitchen. Beautiful dishtowels and pot holders made by Appetite AND made here in Portland, Oregon. Yay!\n\n[caption id="attachment_1512" align="alignnone" width="550" caption="Pot holders - $16.00  Dishtowels- $18.00"]<img class="size-large wp-image-1512" title="dsc_44941" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uplo