(1604, 2, '2009-06-14 12:52:11', '2009-06-14 17:52:11', 'Portlanders have a great love of beer, bikes, coffee...and birds. Thank goodness for our Canadian artists that are more than happy to satisfy the city\'s needs. Gorgeous pieces by Cul de Sac Design, LU Prints and Coe &amp; Waito always makes the bird lovers happy.\n\n[caption id="attachment_1605" align="alignnone" width="550" caption="Pieces by Cul de Sac Design"]<img class="size-large wp-image-1605" title="dsc_4773" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/dsc_4773-550x365.jpg" alt="Pieces by Cul de Sac Design" width="550" height="365" />[/caption]\n\n \n\n[caption id="attachment_1606" align="alignnone" width="550" caption="Large kidney plate by Cul de Sac Design, Bird Bowl by Coe &amp; Waito, and bird coasters by LU Prints."]<img class="size-large wp-image-1606" title="dsc_4767" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/dsc_4767-550x405.jpg" alt="Large kidney plate by Cul de Sac Design, Bird Bowl by Coe &amp; Waito, and bird coasters by LU Prints." width="550" height="405" />[/caption] ', 'The Bird Invasion', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'the-bird-invasion', '', '', '2009-06-14 12:52:11', '2009-06-14 17:52:11', '', 0, 'http://www.elsasam.com/?p=1604', 0, 'post', '', 0),
