(1625, 2, '2009-06-25 12:15:29', '2009-06-25 17:15:29', 'I\'ve been spending the last year debating with myself about painting my door. I was a little burned out after remodeling the shop before I opened and I didn\'t want to touch a paint brush again. Now, one year later, I\'ve finally picked up the brush and given my wobbly ugly door a new look. I\'ve painted it the same shade as the back wall in the shop. Very pleased with the results and very pleased that I can again put that paint brush away.\n\n<img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1626" title="DSC_4837" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/DSC_4837-365x550.jpg" alt="DSC_4837" width="365" height="550" />\n\n<img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1627" title="DSC_4838" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/DSC_4838-550x380.jpg" alt="DSC_4838" width="550" height="380" />', 'my green door', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'my-green-door', '', '', '2009-06-25 12:15:29', '2009-06-25 17:15:29', '', 0, 'http://www.elsasam.com/?p=1625', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(1637, 2, '2009-07-02 16:14:41', '2009-07-02 21:14:41', 'The Swedes take their summertime very seriously after a long winter. It\'s a time to embrace the warmth of the summer air, good company and good food. Here are a few Swedish goodies we have in the shop for your own summertime enjoyment!\n\n[caption id="attachment_1641" align="alignnone" width="550" caption="Handmade butter knives - $12.00 for two"]<img class="size-large wp-image-1641" title="image" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/image1-550x350.jpg" alt="Handmade butter knives - $12.00 for two" width="550" height="350" />[/caption]\n\nGorgeous handmade glassware by Stockholm\'s finest designer, Catarina Giarimi:\n\n[caption id="attachment_1649" align="alignnone" width="227" caption="Seashore lowball glasses- $60.00 for two  Cocktail Pitcher - $70.00"]<img class="size-full wp-image-1649" title="att56bb9" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/att56bb92.jpg" alt="Seashore lowball glasses- $60.00 for two  Cocktail Pitcher - $70.00" width="227" height="227" />[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1650" align="alignnone" width="227" caption="Pineapple Highball glasses - $60.00 for two"]<img class="size-full wp-image-1650" title="att56c0c" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/att56c0c1.jpg" alt="Pineapple Highball glasses - $60.00 for two" width="227" height="227" />[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1651" align="alignnone" width="227" caption="Sunset Martini glasses - $82.00 for two "]<img class="size-full wp-image-1651" title="att373a6" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/att373a63.jpg" alt="Sunset Martini glasses - $82.00 for two " width="227" height="227" />[/caption]\n\nEnjoy teatime with these beautiful porcelain tea sets by Swedish designer, Anna Kraitz:\n\n[caption id="attachment_1654" align="alignnone" width="550" caption="Tea sets - $55.00 each"]<img class="size-large wp-image-1654" title="DSC_4934" src="http://blog.elsasam.