(2412, 2, '2009-12-06 15:54:26', '2009-12-06 20:54:26', '<img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-2416" title="holiday_party_image.1.1" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/holiday_party_image.1.11-449x550.jpg" alt="holiday_party_image.1.1" width="449" height="550" />\n\n \n\nJoin us at elsa+sam for our holiday party on <strong>December 10th from 6- 9pm</strong>. We will also be having an artist reception for local painter, Nikki Hoke Horner. Shoppers can sip on wine and nosh on treats while they <strong>save an extra 15% off </strong>on their entire purchase (including sale items*). This is an excellent way to save on beautiful gifts, enjoy beautiful art, avoid the crazy holiday crowds and simply have a good time!\n\nBest wishes to all of you for a safe and joyous holiday season! We are grateful to have your support!\n\n* Excluding art work.\n\n* Online shoppers: Our stock is limited and may not be updated on a timely matter. Feel free to take 15% off on your entire purchase (plus free shipping) for one day only – December 10th.\n\n<strong>Where:</strong> elsa+sam, 4314 SE Hawthorne Blvd., Portland (<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=4314+SE+Hawthorne+Blvd,+Portland,+OR+97215&amp;sll=45.520842,-122.613945&amp;sspn=0.049794,0.070295&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=addr&amp;ll=45.520842,-122.613945&amp;source=embed">google map</a>)\n<strong>When:</strong> Thursday, December 10th from 6-9pm\n<strong>Contact:</strong> 503-517-9942, <a href="mailto:info@elsasam.com">info@elsasam.com</a>', 'The Holidays are here!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'the-holidays-are-here', '', '', '2009-12-06 15:54:26', '2009-12-06 20:54:26', '', 0, 'http://www.elsasam.com/?p=2412', 0, 'post', '', 0),
