(3570, 2, '2012-01-16 15:37:22', '2012-01-16 23:37:22', 'I have so many favorite pieces in our shop that I want to share! So, I\'ve decided that each week I will post a weekly favorite for everyone to enjoy.\n\nThis week:  Tea Towels by Makelike\n\nThese gorgeous towels are by far one of my favorite pieces! Beautiful, durable, and stunning! All designed by a fabulous company here in Portland, OR. You can use these wonderful towels in your kitchen - they do a wonderful job at cleaning &amp; polishing up glassware or you can simply hang these designs on your wall. Either way, you will love them!\n\nHere are a few of my favorites (in no particular order):\n\n<a href="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/390097_10150449512349806_84578254805_8438039_674537296_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3571" title="390097_10150449512349806_84578254805_8438039_674537296_n" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/390097_10150449512349806_84578254805_8438039_674537296_n-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/388507_10150449512299806_84578254805_8438038_1255624973_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3572" title="388507_10150449512299806_84578254805_8438038_1255624973_n" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/388507_10150449512299806_84578254805_8438038_1255624973_n-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/382630_10150449512424806_84578254805_8438041_1593241895_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3573" title="382630_10150449512424806_84578254805_8438041_1593241895_n" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/382630_10150449512424806_84578254805_8438041_1593241895_n-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /></a>\n\nAll are hand–screenprinted using water–based inks on 100% European linen.\n\nYou can find these towels and more by Makelike <a href="http://www.elsasam.com/index.php?route=product/manufacturer/product&amp;manufacturer_id=23">here</a>.\n\nEnjoy!', 'A favorite... or two... or three....', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'a-favorite-or-two-or-three', '', '', '2012-01-16 15:37:22', '2012-01-16 23:37:22', '', 0, 'http://blog.elsasam.com/?p=3570', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(3585, 2, '2012-01-23 10:17:59', '2012-01-23 18:17:59', 'All the way from Czech Republic by graphic designer Jan Skácelík, these fun prints say it all. Inspired by Scandinavian mid-century design with a simple reminder of how lovely it is to stay warm while sipping on our favorite (morning) beverage.\n\n<a href="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/l-2-500x500.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-3586" title="l-2-500x500" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/l-2-500x500-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/l-1-500x500.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-3587" title="l-1-500x500" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/l-1-500x500-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/l-4-500x500.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-3588" title="l-4-500x500" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/l-4-500x500-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></a>\n\n<div class="clear"></div>\n\nYou can find more here: <a href="http://www.elsasam.com/for-the-home/prints">http://www.elsasam.com/for-the-home/prints</a>', 'Enjoy a cup or two!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'enjoy-a-cup-or-two', '', '', '2012-01-23 10:17:59', '2012-01-23 18:17:59', '', 0, 'http://blog.elsasam.com/?p=3585', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(3603, 2, '2012-02-05 10:16:24', '2012-02-05 18:16:24', 'We love Anthology\'s beautiful magazine. We also love good press! Look for us in their recent issue (#6) on page 9, featuring Geoffrey Lilge\'s amazing handmade cutting boards.\n\n<a href="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/403217_294993293882761_127221323993293_761962_1553901021_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3604" title="403217_294993293882761_127221323993293_761962_1553901021_n" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/403217_294993293882761_127221323993293_761962_1553901021_n-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /></a> <a href="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/IMG_0134.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3605" title="IMG_0134" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/IMG_0134-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></a>', 'Thank you, Anthology Magazine!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'thank-you-anthology-magazine', '', '', '2012-02-05 10:16:24', '2012-02-05 18:16:24', '', 0, 'http://blog.elsasam.com/?p=3603', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(3620, 2, '2012-02-07 09:14:30', '2012-02-07 17:14:30', 'Every year in February, Portlanders get a week\'s worth of spring weather. It\'s wonderful to see the sunlight and see all the little daffodil &amp; tulip sprouts coming out of the ground. You know spring is around the corner but at the same time, you know that it\'s still winter and that this weather is just a pop in visit. *Sigh*\n\nHere are some of my favorite pieces that can brighten the kitchen &amp; home a bit while we wait for spring\'s official arrival.\n\n<a href="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/384745_10150456030704806_84578254805_8456200_145592660_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3627" title="384745_10150456030704806_84578254805_8456200_145592660_n" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/384745_10150456030704806_84578254805_8456200_145592660_n-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Little_geometry_stack.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3628" title="Little_geometry_stack" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Little_geometry_stack-262x300.jpg" alt="" width="262" height="300" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/196996_10150114438159806_84578254805_6285424_3360761_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3622" title="196996_10150114438159806_84578254805_6285424_3360761_n" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/196996_10150114438159806_84578254805_6285424_3360761_n-300x157.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="157" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/381789_10150451479264806_84578254805_8444563_2048913157_n-1.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3624" title="381789_10150451479264806_84578254805_8444563_2048913157_n-1" src="http://blog.elsasam.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/381789_10150451479264806_84578254805_8444563_2048913157_n-1-300x296.jpg" al